<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2777">‌شَرِيكٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5244">‌وَقَيْسٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4311">‌عُثْمَانَ بْنِ عُمَيْرٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2044">‌زَاذَانَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1133">‌جَرِيرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ - صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَلْحِدُوا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَا تَشُقُّوا؛ فَإِنَّ اللَّحْدَ لَنَا وَالشَّقَّ لِغَيْرِنَا».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>